{"tid":2423685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"進食四川火鍋底料恐有致死風險　美國下令回收中國製名揚火鍋底料","createTime":"2021-02-26T05:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T05:14:15.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"11182f59b163a7978437a3d7cdb043ae7caf2dcc","tid":2423685,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2887315/hotpot_thumb_20210226_ch_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2887315%2Fhotpot_thumb_20210226_ch_600.jpg&h=b4ab888d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 美國下令回收10萬磅 「名揚」火鍋底料，指其成分有致死風險。<br />\n<br />\n美國農業部食品安全檢驗局（FSIS）本周一（22日）下令回收近10萬磅中國四川「名揚」火鍋底料，指其含有可致死成分，並敦促已購買該產品的顧客勿食用。TOPick發現，涉事產品於「淘寶網」亦有發售。<br />\n<br />\nFSIS緊急回收含有牛脂成分的「名揚」火鍋底料，指其沒經過複檢，也沒有聯邦檢查的標記。該產品列為最高級的「I級」，即是「一種危害健康的產品，使用後可能引致嚴重健康後果或死亡」。<br />\n<br />\n被回收的三款產品如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2887315/h02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2887315%2Fh02_600.jpg&h=f4177886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「名揚」火鍋底料 牛油微辣（相片來源：FSIS） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2887315/h05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2887315%2Fh05_600.jpg&h=808f9109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「名揚」火鍋底料 牛油特辣（相片來源：FSIS）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2887315/h08_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2887315%2Fh08_600.jpg&h=1e2090e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「名揚」火鍋底料 牛油麻辣（相片來源：FSIS）<br />\n<br />\n美國當局回收約96,810磅「名揚」火鍋底料，涉事產品已被運往亞利桑那州、加州、夏威夷、內華達州、紐約及德州的食肆、分銷商及超市等零售點。FSIS召回等級分為I、II和III三級，涉事產品屬於最高級「I級」，當局敦促已購買該產品的顧客勿食用，應把它們丟棄或退回購買地點。"},{"pid":"6aa76a386062ef9326ac63905b0909544e041fbd","tid":2423685,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"毒品級致命"}]}